    <item>
      <title>外汇损失抵消强劲的旅游需求，靛蓝航空利润未达预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/indigo-s-profit-misses-estimate-despite-strong-travel-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[InterGlobe Aviation Ltd. 是印度市场份额最大的航空公司，该公司报告称季度利润低于预期，原因是外汇相关损失增加抵消了在旅游需求强劲的时期运送更多乘客所带来的收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/indigo-s-profit-misses-estimate-despite-strong-travel-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:43:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法新社称斯里兰卡撤销与阿达尼的购电协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/sri-lanka-revokes-power-purchase-pact-with-adani-group-afp-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据法新社援引未具名政府官员的话称，由于去年美国调查中出现腐败指控，斯里兰卡取消了与印度亿万富翁高塔姆阿达尼企业集团的购电协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/sri-lanka-revokes-power-purchase-pact-with-adani-group-afp-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 08:48:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利因奥尔班的天然气需求而推迟对俄罗斯的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/orban-links-eu-russia-sanctions-renewal-to-ukraine-gas-transit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班呼吁欧盟向乌克兰施压，要求其重新建立俄罗斯向欧洲的天然气输送通道之际，匈牙利延长了对俄罗斯实施制裁的阻挠。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/orban-links-eu-russia-sanctions-renewal-to-ukraine-gas-transit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 07:32:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
